752
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:15,400
It's fine.

753
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:17,270
What happens if we kill him?

754
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,280
If word gets out,

755
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,430
it's indecent

756
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:21,280
for the two of us

757
00:30:21,550 --> 00:30:23,550
to fight a beggar for turf!

758
00:30:24,070 --> 00:30:24,510
Uncle,

759
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:27,490
are we decent now?

760
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:30,700
Wasn't this a pure accident?

761
00:30:31,310 --> 00:30:32,750
That... That guy surnamed Hu.

762
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:33,750
Hu.. What's he called again?

763
00:30:33,750 --> 00:30:34,430
Jianren.

764
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:35,640
Scumbag! (Sounds like Jianren.)

765
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,970
He is the only one
who knows your identity!

766
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:39,530
If Zhou Rong didn't snitch,

767
00:30:39,530 --> 00:30:41,730
