771
00:30:50,210 --> 00:30:51,210
It's despicable!

772
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,880
Call Zhou Rong

773
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,890
and tell him we'll trade tomorrow.

774
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:02,340
Uncle,

775
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:05,030
we don't have the bianzhong anymore.

776
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:06,430
How can we trade with him?

777
00:31:07,110 --> 00:31:09,660
Tomorrow's trade isn't for money.

778
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,970
It's to take his life.

779
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:14,660
Mr. Zhou,

780
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:16,230
no matter what,

781
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,300
we must make this trade tomorrow.

782
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,750
You may rest now.

783
00:31:20,750 --> 00:31:22,150
I'll go prepare the cash.

784
00:31:22,310 --> 00:31:22,640
Wait,

785
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,170
