786
00:31:25,030 --> 00:31:25,560
Mr. Zhou.

787
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:32,680
We can only ask the suppliers for cash.

788
00:31:32,850 --> 00:31:34,920
If I contact a few more,
it should be enough.

789
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:35,830
I'll have them deliver it

790
00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:37,350
to the company tomorrow morning.

791
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,750
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

792
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:39,550
It's nothing.

793
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:42,750
The phone is ringing.

794
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:44,920
Can you answer it?

795
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:56,340
It's Zhu Yifei.

796
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:07,720
Mr. Zhu,

797
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:10,340
why are you still up this late?

798
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:13,170
Mr. Zhou, sorry to bother you.

799
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:15,720
What are you doing right now?

800
00:32:17,350 --> 00:32:18,550
I'm taking a hot bath.

801
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:22,880
He said he's taking a hot bath.

802
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:28,760
Mr. Zhou.

803
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:32,760
We have everything ready.

804
00:32:32,830 --> 00:32:34,310
Let's trade tomorrow.

805
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:40,230
Mr. Zhu, didn't you say

806
00:32:40,230 --> 00:32:42,090
