807
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,130
I was just being impulsive.

808
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,070
Think about it.

809
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:47,590
Who else would I sell it to
other than you?

810
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:52,750
H-How do we trade?

811
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,660
Tomorrow at 10 AM,

812
00:32:54,790 --> 00:32:56,240
we'll meet at the abandoned building

813
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,570
in the western suburbs.

814
00:32:58,110 --> 00:32:59,070
You bring the money here.

815
00:32:59,070 --> 00:33:00,480
Be there or be square.

816
00:33:04,110 --> 00:33:04,770
It's a deal.

817
00:33:12,510 --> 00:33:13,770
What is Zhu Yifei up to?

818
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:16,110
Can you stop asking me

819
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:16,980
questions?

820
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:18,590
Let him do whatever he wants!

821
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:19,760
None of you should

822
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:21,650
ask me any questions today, okay?

823
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:28,840
Mr. Zhou.

824
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:31,800
M-Mr. Zhou...

825
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:33,800
Mr. Zhou.

826
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,680
Can you let me

827
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,160
bathe in the seawater of Gondwana

828
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,920
for a while longer?

829
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:43,240
Okay.

830
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,440
Go on.

831
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:49,890
Go ahead and bathe.

832
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,639
Chief Zhang.

833
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,670
Thank you so much.

834
00:34:32,190 --> 00:34:33,320
National treasure...

835
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:34,800
It is a national treasure!

836
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:36,280
This is what we should do.

837
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:37,400
Chief Zhang,

838
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:39,710
I will compose a poem for you.

839
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,670
What rhyme should I use?

840
00:34:47,250 --> 00:34:48,040
Curator Guo,

841
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:49,010
h-how about this?

842
00:34:49,010 --> 00:34:50,639
Y-You can go to my office.

843
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:51,730
There are pens in my room,

844
00:34:51,730 --> 00:34:52,530
as well as ink.

845
00:34:52,590 --> 00:34:53,960
You can compose a poem anytime.

846
00:34:53,960 --> 00:34:55,820
They still have to solve the case.

847
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:57,960
After the case is solved,

848
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:58,710
