857
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:17,120
[Interrogation Record]

858
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:21,230
[Details of the Interrogation Record]

859
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:25,570
Mao and Xia Tinggang

860
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:28,540
