867
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,890
But we don't know if he's dead or alive.

868
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,800
Then hurry up and go.

869
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:44,880
Have Li Qian go with you.

870
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,410
Yes, sir.

871
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,210
Where is the car?

872
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,140
Where's my car?

873
00:36:44,710 --> 00:36:46,370
Are you sure this is the place?

874
00:36:47,590 --> 00:36:48,510
Y-Yes.

875
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:49,640
Let's go.

876
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:11,290
He should be alive

877
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,740
and probably ran away.

878
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:35,320
Hello?

879
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,060
Who is this?

880
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:38,260
Hello, this is Gao Dong speaking.

881
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:39,480
Chief.

882
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:41,690
It's Director Gao.

883
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:42,890
Don't answer it.

884
00:37:43,070 --> 00:37:44,270
Tell him I'm not here.

885
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:47,560
Director Gao, Chief Zhang said he's...

886
00:37:49,790 --> 00:37:50,590
Here he comes.

887
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:53,310
Director Gao.

888
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:55,530
The interrogation's over.

889
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,920
These two people should have nothing

890
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:59,450
to do with Zhou Rong's case.

891
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:00,670
And they probably have nothing

892
00:38:00,670 --> 00:38:02,530
to do with Liu Bei's death either.

893
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,440
But we did find something.

894
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:05,440
We found the bianzhong,

895
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,440
the complete set.

896
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:07,550
The antique trafficker is called
Zhu Yifei.

897
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:08,800
We've issued an arrest warrant.

898
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:10,460
Huo Zheng works for Zhu Yifei.

899
00:38:11,630 --> 00:38:13,230
What about Fang Chao and Liu Zhi?

900
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,560
Still looking for them.

901
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,110
Can you give me a result

902
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:17,150
by noon today?

903
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,250
Now...

904
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:22,920
He wants us to give him a result by noon.

905
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:23,960
Then recite poetry.

906
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:24,490
Sit down.

907
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,080
Director Gao,

908
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:28,450
this is Li Qian.

909
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:31,220
I have something to report to you.

910
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:32,330
Go ahead.

911
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,960
Letting Fang Chao and Liu Zhi go

912
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,560
wasn't Chief Zhang's fault.

913
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:41,710
Song Xing and I acted
without authorization,

914
00:38:41,710 --> 00:38:43,170
which is why they got away.

915
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:44,960
Chief Zhang said that

916
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,510
just so we wouldn't feel pressured.

917
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:48,110
He's taking the blame for us.

918
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:49,550
Stop it.

919
00:38:49,670 --> 00:38:50,880
Everything Li Qian said is true.

920
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:51,800
If you hadn't talked nonsense,

921
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,550
would the Chief have been pushed
to this extent?

922
00:38:53,550 --> 00:38:54,350
Director Gao,

923
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,760
what you're doing

924
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:57,160
is unfair to Chief Zhang.

925
00:38:57,710 --> 00:38:58,510
If someone has to be punished,

926
00:38:58,510 --> 00:38:59,710
it should be us first.

927
00:39:16,510 --> 00:39:18,070
So, regarding the deadline
to catch Zhou Rong,

928
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:19,530
can it be extended a bit...

929
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:20,670
Hello, Director Gao.

930
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:22,030
We can catch Zhou Rong by noon today.

931
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:23,230
I'll get back to work.

932
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:24,800
Get the surveillance footage

933
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:26,070
of Lu Yibo leaving the Municipal Bureau

934
00:39:26,070 --> 00:39:26,800
yesterday.

935
00:39:34,620 --> 00:39:38,240
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]
[Gate 2]

936
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:38,800
Pause.

937
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:44,540
Investigate this car.

938
00:39:54,130 --> 00:39:57,740
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

939
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,300
It's Rongcheng Group's car.

940
00:39:59,230 --> 00:39:59,630
Right.

941
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,760
That makes sense.

942
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:01,630
Lu Yibo drove his own car

943
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:02,630
when he came yesterday.

944
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:03,360
When he left,

945
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,110
he got into Rongcheng Group's car.

946
00:40:05,110 --> 00:40:06,110
Zhou Rong wanted to know

947
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,500
what Lu Yibo told us.

948
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:09,200
Lu Yibo stayed at our bureau

949
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:09,890
for a day,

950
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:11,120
and we didn't see him.

951
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:11,920
If he went back

952
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:13,190
and told Zhou Rong that,

953
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,960
Zhou Rong definitely wouldn't believe it.

954
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:15,740
After all,

955
00:40:16,070 --> 00:40:18,200
Lu Yibo has a history of betraying him.

956
00:40:20,110 --> 00:40:22,110
Even the most impregnable fortress

957
00:40:22,110 --> 00:40:24,000
cannot withstand an internal collapse.

958
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,280
So their mistrust of each other

959
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,810
is our breakthrough point.

960
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:27,960
Song Xing.

961
00:40:28,320 --> 00:40:29,230
You're the biggest contributor

962
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:29,760
to this case.

963
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,230
Really?

964
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:32,750
We'll go find Lu Yibo now.

965
00:40:32,750 --> 00:40:33,280
No.

966
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:35,640
We're going to visit Lang Bowen.

967
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,130
Everyone is going.

968
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:43,030
How unpredictable.

969
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:45,480
Look!

970
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:54,000
What happened?

971
00:40:54,190 --> 00:40:55,850
So many police cars have come!

972
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:56,940
With all this fuss,

973
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:59,290
something big must have happened.

974
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:06,760
Chief Zhang,

975
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,680
do we need so many people?

976
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:11,220
Are there many?

977
00:41:12,110 --> 00:41:12,630
No.

978
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,940
You keep watch here

979
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:49,670
and don't let anyone get close.

980
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:50,110
Yes, sir.
